import { Divider } from "@material-ui/core"
import MainInput from "./MainInput"

const MainForm = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <Divider />
                <MainInput type="datetime-local"/>
                <MainInput type="datetime-local"/>
                <MainInput type="text"/>
            <Divider />
        </>
    )
}

export default MainForm
